      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIGHT WORK (4) has been edging towards a win, the latest when runner-up behind dominant winner Khaleesi's Dream. Meets a lesser line-up here and can get off the mark. ALLA RUSTICA (1) was solid fresh then gassed early last time trying to hold the front on the inside. Wobbled around corner and faded to finish sixth in the same race as LIGHT WORK. Blinkers added and fitter can improve sharply. AWESOME ORPHAN (3) is drawn to stalk the pace and gets chance to find form. NEED A GIGGLE (2) was another out of the Khaleesi's Dream race, finishing third. Only needs to run up to that to be in the finish of this. STRATOVISION (8) ran fourth in the same race and is next best.",
